%% Diagram: Keyboard drag state machine
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle: focused item
    Idle: announce instructions on focus
    Idle --> Grabbed: Enter or Space
    Grabbed: target = current index
    Grabbed: announce "Grabbed item N of M"
    Grabbed --> Grabbed: ArrowUp / ArrowDown / ArrowLeft / ArrowRight
    Grabbed --> Idle: Escape
    Grabbed --> Dropped: Enter or Space
    Dropped: commit reorder fromIndex to toIndex
    Dropped: announce "Dropped at position N"
    Dropped --> Idle
